skins.shipDescription: C-class destroyer ` Cygnet, Hull Number H83!
skins.selfIntroduction: I-I'm the C-class's Cygnet... Before I went abroad, I had always been in the Home Fleet... I may not look like it but... I'm good at fishing! Uh... I... I'll do my best!
skins.acquisition: I am... I'm the C-class destroyer Cygnet... yes! For the sake of getting fish and chips, I will do my best!
skins.login: C-Commander... you've finally come~ This place is huge... I was lost...
skins.details: Uwee~ This is so embarrassing... Why do I have strike such a pose...
skins.secretaryIdle1: You're always so quiet, Commander. I'm sleepy. ZZZZ... Huh? I... I-I'm not sleeping!
skins.secretaryIdle2: What do I like...? I'm too embarrassed to say it... Eh? I-It's an order? I... I like to eat delicious meals
skins.secretaryIdle3: That girl's clothes are so beautiful... Eh? No no no! I-I'm just complimenting, s-s-so I don't think those clothes will suit me!
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Commander... I don't understand... Why am I getting hotter?

skins.shipDescription: This outfit is a little tight... Yes, really? I understand. I've got to work harder for the Royal Navy!
skins.acquisition: These clothes are tight after all... I-Is that so? I see! For the sake of having the royal cuisine, I will work harder!
skins.secretaryIdle1: I'm relaxed when I'm next to you, Commander... Eh? I-I haven't said anything! You must've heard something!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Commander... umm... that... we've run out of fish and chips... Can we... go buy them?
skins.secretaryIdle3: I'm cute? I-I-I-I'm totally not cute! Ugh... You're making fun of me, Commander!
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: E-even I... am not oblivious to all things! ...B-but if it's you, Commander...

skins.shipDescription: Well, the swimsuit that Hood gave to me is a little tight, don't you think? Want to play beach volleyball? Do you think... can we win?
skins.acquisition: Ooh... the swimwear that Hood gave me is a little tight... Huh? Play beace volleyball with Sara...? Am I... gonna win...?
skins.login: C-Commander, welcome back~ Haa... Air conditioners are such wonderful inventions... Phew... This feels nice...
skins.details: Hood gave this swimwear to me as a present but, how is it?... It's not inappropriate for me, right?
skins.secretaryIdle1: Ah Hood, you are the most beautiful thing in the world! I feel a bit ashamed.... Hwe... This punishment is so embarrassing...
skins.secretaryIdle2: The barbecue party happens after sunset... Ehehe, I'm looking forward to that as well~
skins.secretaryIdle3: Sara's face darkened when she saw me... Do you think she dislikes me?...
skins.secretaryTouch: Commander, are you going to take a picture of me?
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Wah! Commander, my... my swimwear is tight, so... please don't touch it, ok?

skins.shipDescription: H-happy Christmas! A-after that... umm... I have this present for ya, Commander...
skins.acquisition: H-happy Christmas! A-after that... umm... I have this present for ya, Commander...
skins.secretaryIdle1: Christmas feast! I-it's a real Christmas feast! Haah... I wanna stuff mahself silly?
skins.secretaryIdle2: Hawawa... for some reason, I'm not gettin' full no matter how much I eat today...
skins.secretaryIdle3: Uuu... Hood? I'm not a real cygnet... even if I don't eat this much, I'm still not flyin'...
skins.secretaryTouch: My tummy is sticking out? N-no way that's true... Ugh... startin' tomorrow, I'm gonna go on a diet... Startin' tomorrow...
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Ah, um... Please... don't do that... Uuuu...

skins.shipDescription: Aww... it took me a while to get changed... Commander, did I keep you waiting long? Hehe... th-that's good. Let's get going, then~
skins.acquisition: Aww... it took me a while to get changed... Hope I didn't keep ya waitin' too long, Commander? Hehe... th-that's good. Let's get goin', then~
skins.login: There you are, Commander! I was worried ya lost me...
skins.details: Comet and Crescent picked this outfit for me, but... ain't it a bit too showy? Erm... it's too much, innit? Um... n-never mind!
skins.secretaryIdle1: It's so cold I'd rather stay inside and eat fish and chips come wintertime... But goin' out with you's pretty nice too!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Commander, I heard there's gonna be one of them fireworks shows for New Year's! What say we go together?
skins.secretaryIdle3: Commander, umm... what do ya think of me, Comet, and Crescent doin' like a New Year's concert for ya all dressed up like this in Sakura Empire clothes?
skins.secretaryTouch: Hold your hand so I don't get lost?! Erm, um, uh, I think holdin' your sleeve's good enough, Commandeeer...!

skins.shipDescription: G-Good day, Master... C-Commander, please don't stare at me so much... Uuu... Saratoga told me that this was part of marketin' yourself as an idol...
skins.acquisition: G-Good day, Master... C-Commander, please don't stare at me so much... Uuu... Saratoga told me that this was part of marketin' yourself as an idol...
skins.details: I thought I'd understand if I tried for myself but, the Maid Team really amazing... Compared to them, I'm just... Uuu...
skins.secretaryIdle1: Commander is looking at me... Uu... I don't think these frilly clothes suit me after all...
skins.secretaryIdle2: Eek! ...S-sorry, Commander, I knocked over the bucket again... Uuu...
skins.secretaryIdle3: "Do your best, Cygnet! I know you'll be able to do it" ...That's what Saratoga told me, so I'll have to work harder...!
skins.secretaryTouch: Umm... "Thank you for all your support!" ...Speak up, and b-bend forward a bit...? I, I don't think I can do that...
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Eeep?! .......S-Sorry, Commander! I wasn't trying to hit you with the mop on purpose...

skins.shipDescription: C-Commander? Erm... They picked me to be a cheerleader for the Royal Navy team at the sports thing, so I'm practicin' my cheers... D-don't stare at me like that... I'm shy enough... Already...
skins.acquisition: C-Commander? Erm... They picked me to be a cheerleader for the Royal Navy team at the sports thing, so I'm practicin' my cheers... D-don't stare at me like that... I'm shy enough... Already...
skins.login: I heard it was Hood who said I should be a cheerleader... So I won't let her down...! But these moves ain't easy... Maybe it shouldn't be me...
skins.details: If I cock this up, it'll make Hood and the whole Royal Navy look bad... You believe in me, Commander? I-I'll do my best then!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Craven did her best to teach me how to cheer, but I'm still not very good...
skins.secretaryIdle2: Ships of the Royal Navy! And everyone on the field! Umm, gooooooooo...! I need to be louder?! I really don't think I can...
skins.secretaryIdle3: Saratoga says idols have to be "multi-talented"! S-so I have to do this! I will!
skins.secretaryTouch: Aiieee...?! That was close... If you didn't catch me, Commander, I would've fallen right over...
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: I'm feelin' kinda funny... M-must be I'm too tired is all?
